title: Blue Stahli - BSides and Other Things I Forgot and Carve Reprise
description:
This is the Blue Stahli album BSides and Other Things I Forgot and the recent Blue Stahli reprise of Josh Money's Carve straight from the fixt store.  I waited to upload this to encourage people to pay for this music as it is so cheap ($8.98!!!).


All kidding aside go buy the music if you liked it.  Bret thanks you(though he probably wants me to die in a fire).
